title: About me
text: Hi, my name is Aidan Astridge and I’m a recently graduated professional with an Honours Bachelor of Commerce from York University focusing on the domains of Data Analysis and Management Science. I love to learn new libraries in R, Python, and SAS for hypothesis testing, clustering, classification, regression, optimization, and time-series analysis.
